Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:02.72,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Hello, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:06.12,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.61,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Şükran, come sit next to Şüray for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:09.48,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:11.72,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:14.19,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,No, sir, not even a drop of water—we don’t want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:15.98,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,There's a pair of pants there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.78,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,The pipe is yours now—congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:21.07,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to do with the water; it’s because of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.01,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Are you free?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:23.89,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,So, do I belong here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:24.89,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,It's in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.23,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,What kind of plow should we use?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:28.69,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,You saw us in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:30.14,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Did you think he was a gardener?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:31.92,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,I am Özgür, my driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:33.46,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,Wise, wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.67,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,I also remember the world middleweight boxing champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:37.70,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,It's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:39.93,Dinamik,,0,0,0,,That looks nice.
